title: Iran's Supreme Leader shown at event amid reports of deteriorating health
description: Iran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Seyyed Ali Khamenei was seen attending an event at a mosque in Tehran on Saturday, according to pictures and a video published on Iran's government websites and state media, one day after reports circulated about of his deteriorating health.

title: 3.4 million children in Pakistan need 'immediate, lifesaving support' after floods: UNICEF
description: "Super floods" in Pakistan have left 3.4 million children in need of "immediate, lifesaving support," according to UNICEF.

title: As Singapore mourns the Queen, there's little discussion about its colonial past
description: It has been close to six decades since the British monarchy symbolically ruled Singapore, but Queen Elizabeth II's death still elicited grief and reflection in the Southeast Asian nation.
